1
00:00:10,984 --> 00:00:20,069
<font color="#06cdf8">jmg subs</font>

2
00:00:50,383 --> 00:00:52,418
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>You know nothing.</i></b></font>

3
00:00:56,222 --> 00:00:59,892
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>His father was Zeus. The Zeus.</i></b></font>

4
00:00:59,894 --> 00:01:02,194
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>King of the gods.</i></b></font>

5
00:01:04,798 --> 00:01:09,501
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>His mother,
alcmene, a mortal woman.</i></b></font>

6
00:01:10,937 --> 00:01:13,238
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>Together, they had a boy.</i></b></font>

7
00:01:13,506 --> 00:01:15,174
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>Half human,</i></b></font>

8
00:01:15,508 --> 00:01:17,709
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>half God.</i></b></font>

9
00:01:19,512 --> 00:01:24,783
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>But Zeus' queen, hera, saw
this bastard child as an insult,</i></b></font>

10
00:01:24,785 --> 00:01:28,854
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>a living reminder of
her husband's infidelity.</i></b></font>

11
00:01:28,856 --> 00:01:31,824
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>Alcmene named
the boy Hercules,</i></b></font>

12
00:01:31,826 --> 00:01:33,959
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>which means "glory of hera,"</i></b></font>

13
00:01:33,961 --> 00:01:37,763
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>but this failed to
appease the goddess.</i></b></font>

14
00:01:37,765 --> 00:01:40,766
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>She wanted him dead.</i></b></font>

15
00:01:59,386 --> 00:02:02,688
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>Luckily,
he took after his father.</i></b></font>

16
00:02:04,290 --> 00:02:05,357
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>Once he reached manhood,</i></b></font>

17
00:02:05,359 --> 00:02:09,094
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>the gods commanded him
to perform twelve labors,</i></b></font>

18
00:02:09,096 --> 00:02:11,563
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>twelve dangerous missions.</i></b></font>

19
00:02:11,565 --> 00:02:14,133
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>If he completed
them all and survived,</i></b></font>

20
00:02:14,135 --> 00:02:17,903
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>hera agreed to finally
let him live in peace.</i></b></font>

21
00:02:36,022 --> 00:02:39,191
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>He fought the lernean hydra!</i></b></font>

22
00:02:51,906 --> 00:02:55,307
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>He battled
the erymanthean boar!</i></b></font>

23
00:03:07,453 --> 00:03:11,757
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>But his greatest labor
was the nemean lion.</i></b></font>

24
00:03:16,496 --> 00:03:19,565
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>This was no ordinary beast.</i></b></font>

25
00:03:21,635 --> 00:03:26,038
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>It had a hide so tough,
no weapon could penetrate it.</i></b></font>

26
00:03:37,417 --> 00:03:42,721
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>But even this monster was
no match for the son of Zeus.</i></b></font>

27
00:03:45,992 --> 00:03:47,693
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What a load of crap!</b></font>

28
00:03:47,695 --> 00:03:49,461
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Every word is true.</b></font>

29
00:03:51,698 --> 00:03:53,865
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You know what I think?</b></font>

30
00:03:53,867 --> 00:03:57,135
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This friend of yours
doesn't even exist.</b></font>

31
00:03:58,272 --> 00:03:58,971
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Laugh all you want.</b></font>

32
00:03:58,973 --> 00:04:04,042
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He's coming. And be warned,
gryza, he despises pirates.</b></font>

33
00:04:04,177 --> 00:04:06,111
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Macedonia has been good to us.</b></font>

34
00:04:06,113 --> 00:04:09,481
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Plenty of villages
ripe for pillaging.</b></font>

35
00:04:09,483 --> 00:04:11,049
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We are here to stay.</b></font>

36
00:04:11,051 --> 00:04:12,584
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Finish him.</b></font>

37
00:04:14,822 --> 00:04:18,190
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The more you struggle,
the faster you drop.</b></font>

38
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:22,427
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Indeed, your fleet is strong.
I...</b></font>

39
00:04:24,764 --> 00:04:30,469
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Yet, as I was about to explain
before I was so rudely interrupted,</b></font>

40
00:04:30,471 --> 00:04:33,105
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>the nemean lion
was strong, too.</b></font>

41
00:04:33,339 --> 00:04:34,840
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Yet, he still destroyed it.</b></font>

42
00:04:34,842 --> 00:04:39,778
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And not with a sword
or a spear or arrows. No!</b></font>

43
00:04:43,182 --> 00:04:45,851
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I did it with my bare hands!</b></font>

44
00:04:48,821 --> 00:04:50,489
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Or so they say.</b></font>

45
00:04:53,326 --> 00:04:54,793
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules.</b></font>

46
00:04:54,795 --> 00:04:56,495
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Is this all the men you have?</b></font>

47
00:04:56,497 --> 00:04:59,031
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>There's 40 of us. One of you.</b></font>

48
00:04:59,033 --> 00:05:03,969
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The king of this land has
offered me gold to dispose of you.</b></font>

49
00:05:03,971 --> 00:05:06,638
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>So leave, or die.</b></font>

50
00:05:06,640 --> 00:05:08,807
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I get paid either way.</b></font>

51
00:05:09,242 --> 00:05:11,877
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Make him bleed.</b></font>

52
00:05:18,351 --> 00:05:20,118
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Five men with a single blow.</b></font>

53
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:23,455
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Still think you can destroy
the son of Zeus?</b></font>

54
00:05:23,457 --> 00:05:25,691
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Bring me his head!</b></font>

55
00:05:27,860 --> 00:05:30,629
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Seems they need
more convincing, autolycus.</b></font>

56
00:05:30,631 --> 00:05:32,464
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>That's why we're here.</b></font>

57
00:05:34,034 --> 00:05:36,868
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Atalanta.</b></font>

58
00:05:39,172 --> 00:05:40,539
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Amphiaraus.</b></font>

59
00:05:43,209 --> 00:05:44,343
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>May Zeus forgive you.</b></font>

60
00:05:44,345 --> 00:05:46,645
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Tydeus?</b></font>

61
00:06:09,369 --> 00:06:10,435
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Die, Hercules!</b></font>

62
00:06:15,675 --> 00:06:18,510
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Ah, good man.</b></font>

63
00:06:29,223 --> 00:06:30,455
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hurry!</b></font>

64
00:06:30,723 --> 00:06:32,190
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hurry! Uncle!</b></font>

65
00:06:34,094 --> 00:06:35,394
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Uncle, hurry!</b></font>

66
00:06:35,396 --> 00:06:37,329
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hurry! Hurry!</b></font>

67
00:06:40,733 --> 00:06:41,633
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Any longer, Uncle...</b></font>

68
00:06:41,635 --> 00:06:45,771
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And the girls would finally
be safe from your attentions.</b></font>

69
00:06:49,475 --> 00:06:51,543
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The rest of you may go.</b></font>

70
00:06:52,278 --> 00:06:54,012
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But not you.</b></font>

71
00:07:05,992 --> 00:07:07,793
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Thirteen,</b></font>

72
00:07:08,027 --> 00:07:10,896
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>14, 15, 16,</b></font>

73
00:07:10,898 --> 00:07:15,233
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>-17, 18, 19, 20.
- That was fun.</b></font>

74
00:07:15,235 --> 00:07:18,670
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Twenty pirates
at two gold pieces a head,</b></font>

75
00:07:18,672 --> 00:07:21,373
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>minus the headless ones.
Let's see.</b></font>

76
00:07:21,375 --> 00:07:21,807
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Not a bad night.</b></font>

77
00:07:21,809 --> 00:07:25,710
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You see how the pirates ran?
My story softened their resolve.</b></font>

78
00:07:25,712 --> 00:07:28,313
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Their resolve must
be broken, iolaus.</b></font>

79
00:07:28,315 --> 00:07:30,348
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>When you spread
the legend of Hercules,</b></font>

80
00:07:30,350 --> 00:07:32,017
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>make it bigger, scarier.</b></font>

81
00:07:32,019 --> 00:07:35,287
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The more they believe Hercules
is truly the son of Zeus,</b></font>

82
00:07:35,289 --> 00:07:37,789
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>the less likely
they are to fight.</b></font>

83
00:07:38,157 --> 00:07:39,858
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Oh!</b></font>

84
00:07:40,827 --> 00:07:42,594
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Aye.</b></font>

85
00:07:43,329 --> 00:07:45,263
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Amphiaraus?
- Mmm?</b></font>

86
00:07:45,265 --> 00:07:47,532
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Care to join us here on earth?</b></font>

87
00:07:51,170 --> 00:07:57,576
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>A lion and a crow in strange alliance,
fighting across a sea of corpses.</b></font>

88
00:08:02,515 --> 00:08:07,319
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>If you're going to use those
herbs, amphiaraus, at least share.</b></font>

89
00:08:07,321 --> 00:08:08,620
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Huh?</b></font>

90
00:08:13,060 --> 00:08:18,296
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Thug: Hold it!
Hold it! Hold it! Hold it!</b></font>

91
00:08:18,298 --> 00:08:20,899
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Fight it!</b></font>

92
00:08:21,567 --> 00:08:23,034
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Keep practicing, boys!</b></font>

93
00:08:23,036 --> 00:08:26,338
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>So who's next? You? You?</b></font>

94
00:08:26,340 --> 00:08:27,639
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Ah!</b></font>

95
00:08:29,642 --> 00:08:30,709
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>That's a pretty sight.</b></font>

96
00:08:30,711 --> 00:08:33,144
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>One more payday, autolycus,
that's all we need.</b></font>

97
00:08:33,146 --> 00:08:36,748
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Then we get to live like
the kings we've served.</b></font>

98
00:08:36,750 --> 00:08:39,351
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Or live simply.</b></font>

99
00:08:40,486 --> 00:08:42,587
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You still dreaming
of barbarian lands?</b></font>

100
00:08:42,589 --> 00:08:45,757
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Beyond the aegean. At the
shores of the black sea.</b></font>

101
00:08:45,759 --> 00:08:50,061
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>That is where I will live out
the rest of my days in solitude.</b></font>

102
00:08:50,063 --> 00:08:51,997
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Boring, if you ask me.</b></font>

103
00:08:51,999 --> 00:08:52,564
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Maybe so, autolycus.</b></font>

104
00:08:52,566 --> 00:08:57,636
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But I'll never find peace unless
I move as far away as possible.</b></font>

105
00:08:58,538 --> 00:08:58,970
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What of tydeus?</b></font>

106
00:08:58,972 --> 00:09:03,041
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Without you to temper his
rage, I fear what he may become.</b></font>

107
00:09:03,043 --> 00:09:04,442
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Tydeus will go with me.</b></font>

108
00:09:04,444 --> 00:09:08,113
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Civilization has become
too civilized for us.</b></font>

109
00:09:08,115 --> 00:09:09,514
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Uncle!</b></font>

110
00:09:09,582 --> 00:09:13,585
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Join us. The girls are
eager to welcome you.</b></font>

111
00:09:21,561 --> 00:09:24,629
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>See?
I told you I knew Hercules.</b></font>

112
00:09:26,065 --> 00:09:27,532
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Are you his servant?</b></font>

113
00:09:27,534 --> 00:09:29,100
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm his nephew.</b></font>

114
00:09:29,102 --> 00:09:29,968
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Are you, really?</b></font>

115
00:09:29,970 --> 00:09:31,336
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I tell of
Hercules' twelve labors,</b></font>

116
00:09:31,338 --> 00:09:34,639
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>like the nemean lion,
the apples of the hesperides,</b></font>

117
00:09:34,641 --> 00:09:35,206
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>the belt of hippolyta</b></font>

118
00:09:35,208 --> 00:09:38,076
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>with its buxom naked Amazons
and exciting bondage.</b></font>

119
00:09:38,078 --> 00:09:41,813
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- I immortalize him...
- He talks, while the rest of us fight.</b></font>

120
00:09:41,815 --> 00:09:45,417
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It is a wonder you share
the same blood as Hercules.</b></font>

121
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,553
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Have fun.</b></font>

122
00:09:48,688 --> 00:09:50,589
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Ladies.
- Both: Oh...</b></font>

123
00:10:10,242 --> 00:10:12,043
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What do you
want with Hercules?</b></font>

124
00:10:12,045 --> 00:10:13,812
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My words are for him, not you.</b></font>

125
00:10:13,814 --> 00:10:16,615
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Atalanta, it's all right.</b></font>

126
00:10:22,288 --> 00:10:24,723
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You certainly are
a hard man to find.</b></font>

127
00:10:24,725 --> 00:10:27,092
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Maybe I don't want
anyone to find me.</b></font>

128
00:10:27,094 --> 00:10:28,593
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm not just anyone.</b></font>

129
00:10:28,595 --> 00:10:31,429
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My name is ergenia,
daughter to lord cotys.</b></font>

130
00:10:31,431 --> 00:10:35,433
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Your father is most fortunate
to have such a beautiful heir.</b></font>

131
00:10:36,869 --> 00:10:39,270
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My father is most unfortunate.</b></font>

132
00:10:39,272 --> 00:10:42,073
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He battles a warlord, rhesus.</b></font>

133
00:10:42,075 --> 00:10:43,241
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Our land is torn by civil war.</b></font>

134
00:10:43,243 --> 00:10:47,479
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Every day, villages are destroyed,
crops ruined, innocents slaughtered.</b></font>

135
00:10:47,481 --> 00:10:49,447
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We all have problems.</b></font>

136
00:10:49,515 --> 00:10:55,387
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well, perhaps I can convince you
to make our problems your own.</b></font>

137
00:10:56,188 --> 00:10:56,955
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Unfortunately, my lady,</b></font>

138
00:10:56,957 --> 00:11:00,325
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules is fully committed
till the feast of dionysus.</b></font>

139
00:11:00,426 --> 00:11:00,992
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We could, however,</b></font>

140
00:11:00,994 --> 00:11:05,130
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>advance you to the front of
the line, for the right price.</b></font>

141
00:11:05,132 --> 00:11:05,897
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hmm.</b></font>

142
00:11:05,899 --> 00:11:07,699
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I thought heroes
fight for glory.</b></font>

143
00:11:07,701 --> 00:11:09,868
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But mercenaries
fight for gold.</b></font>

144
00:11:09,870 --> 00:11:11,836
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Lord cotys is a rich man.</b></font>

145
00:11:11,838 --> 00:11:12,404
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I like him already.</b></font>

146
00:11:12,406 --> 00:11:17,308
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>If you agree to aid him, he
will pay your weight in gold.</b></font>

147
00:11:20,913 --> 00:11:22,547
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Eat up.</b></font>

148
00:11:27,420 --> 00:11:30,689
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>"A lion and crow in
strange alliance."</b></font>

149
00:11:30,990 --> 00:11:32,857
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Told you.</b></font>

150
00:11:37,930 --> 00:11:40,265
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Where are we going?</b></font>

151
00:12:41,093 --> 00:12:43,394
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It is good to see
you safe, my lady.</b></font>

152
00:12:46,132 --> 00:12:50,535
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This war claims more victims every
day. We were concerned, my lady.</b></font>

153
00:12:50,537 --> 00:12:54,606
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Thank you, general sitacles.
I was well protected.</b></font>

154
00:12:54,608 --> 00:12:55,640
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Ah.</b></font>

155
00:12:55,642 --> 00:12:59,410
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The mighty Hercules. An honor.</b></font>

156
00:13:00,312 --> 00:13:03,548
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Though not quite as big
an honor as I expected.</b></font>

157
00:13:03,749 --> 00:13:07,619
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>General, go tell my father
Hercules is here.</b></font>

158
00:13:10,990 --> 00:13:14,692
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Uncle? Hera. Impressive.</b></font>

159
00:13:14,694 --> 00:13:15,326
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It's meant to be.</b></font>

160
00:13:15,328 --> 00:13:19,497
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It took five years and a
thousand men to build her temple.</b></font>

161
00:13:19,499 --> 00:13:21,499
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hera is the patron
goddess of thrace.</b></font>

162
00:13:21,501 --> 00:13:25,837
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Everyone knows the legend, how
hera seeks to destroy Hercules.</b></font>

163
00:13:25,839 --> 00:13:30,341
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Perhaps the right cause
might finally reconcile you.</b></font>

164
00:13:30,343 --> 00:13:31,876
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Mother!</b></font>

165
00:13:31,977 --> 00:13:33,511
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Arius.</b></font>

166
00:13:36,248 --> 00:13:38,483
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- You're Hercules.
- That's right.</b></font>

167
00:13:38,485 --> 00:13:41,352
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My name is arius. I know
all your labors by heart.</b></font>

168
00:13:41,354 --> 00:13:44,122
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You killed the giant geryon
with a single blow,</b></font>

169
00:13:44,124 --> 00:13:46,191
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>cleaned the augean stables
in one night.</b></font>

170
00:13:46,193 --> 00:13:46,891
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules is probably tired.</b></font>

171
00:13:46,893 --> 00:13:48,793
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And the labor of the hide,
and the labor of the mares.</b></font>

172
00:13:48,795 --> 00:13:51,429
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- That's enough, arius.
Come along.</b></font>

173
00:13:51,497 --> 00:13:52,363
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Stay away from him.</b></font>

174
00:13:52,365 --> 00:13:55,300
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Men who deal in violence
attract violence.</b></font>

175
00:13:55,302 --> 00:13:59,537
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But he's Hercules. He's no
mere mortal. He's the greatest!</b></font>

176
00:14:01,874 --> 00:14:04,475
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Lord cotys will see you now.</b></font>

177
00:14:10,783 --> 00:14:13,685
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Have you ever met royalty,
Hercules?</b></font>

178
00:14:14,220 --> 00:14:16,654
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Once or twice.</b></font>

179
00:14:32,805 --> 00:14:35,573
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Both: Father!
- Ah!</b></font>

180
00:14:39,945 --> 00:14:41,279
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Megara.</b></font>

181
00:14:43,949 --> 00:14:45,950
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Welcome home, my love.</b></font>

182
00:14:52,358 --> 00:14:53,958
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules!</b></font>

183
00:14:56,562 --> 00:15:00,999
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Whenever I'm here, I imagine this
is what elysium must look like.</b></font>

184
00:15:01,001 --> 00:15:02,867
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well, men like us
have the means</b></font>

185
00:15:02,869 --> 00:15:06,704
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>to create our own
paradise on earth.</b></font>

186
00:15:06,706 --> 00:15:07,906
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Look.</b></font>

187
00:15:07,908 --> 00:15:09,941
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Magnificent, aren't they?</b></font>

188
00:15:10,342 --> 00:15:15,546
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well, do not keep us in suspense.
Are we safe from the monster hydra?</b></font>

189
00:15:17,583 --> 00:15:20,385
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The hydra's heads,
your majesty.</b></font>

190
00:15:27,860 --> 00:15:30,528
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The masks of serpents.</b></font>

191
00:15:30,763 --> 00:15:33,598
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No wonder men thought
they were monsters.</b></font>

192
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:37,068
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You've done your sovereign
a great service. Come.</b></font>

193
00:15:37,369 --> 00:15:39,237
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Let the people
have their hero.</b></font>

194
00:15:39,239 --> 00:15:43,675
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Male servant:
All hail king eurystheus.</b></font>

195
00:15:43,677 --> 00:15:46,844
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And the mighty
protector of Athens,</b></font>

196
00:15:46,846 --> 00:15:49,747
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules!</b></font>

197
00:15:50,783 --> 00:15:52,850
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules! Hercules! Hercules!</b></font>

198
00:15:52,852 --> 00:15:58,556
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>A man faced with such adoration might
be tempted to think himself a God.</b></font>

199
00:15:59,725 --> 00:16:03,061
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I only want to be
a husband and a father.</b></font>

200
00:16:10,336 --> 00:16:12,270
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Lord cotys awaits.</b></font>

201
00:16:31,357 --> 00:16:33,691
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules.</b></font>

202
00:16:35,027 --> 00:16:36,594
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Welcome.</b></font>

203
00:16:36,929 --> 00:16:40,565
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>An honor to
host such a legend.</b></font>

204
00:16:40,699 --> 00:16:42,734
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Lord cotys.</b></font>

205
00:16:43,435 --> 00:16:46,471
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But in legend,
you fight alone.</b></font>

206
00:16:46,473 --> 00:16:50,742
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My reputation would not exist
without my comrades.</b></font>

207
00:16:51,677 --> 00:16:53,311
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Autolycus of sparta.</b></font>

208
00:16:55,247 --> 00:16:57,415
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Tydeus of thebes.</b></font>

209
00:16:59,385 --> 00:17:01,185
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Atalanta of scythia.</b></font>

210
00:17:02,121 --> 00:17:04,288
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Iolaus of Athens.</b></font>

211
00:17:04,690 --> 00:17:07,291
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And amphiaraus of argos.</b></font>

212
00:17:07,293 --> 00:17:08,893
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Amphiaraus?</b></font>

213
00:17:10,596 --> 00:17:12,797
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The famed seer of argos.</b></font>

214
00:17:12,799 --> 00:17:15,199
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It is said you have glimpsed
your own death,</b></font>

215
00:17:15,201 --> 00:17:19,871
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>so you fight each battle knowing
that it is not yet your time to die.</b></font>

216
00:17:19,873 --> 00:17:22,273
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What else can you
tell of the future?</b></font>

217
00:17:22,275 --> 00:17:25,777
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Only what the gods
see fit to reveal.</b></font>

218
00:17:25,779 --> 00:17:26,344
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>A shame.</b></font>

219
00:17:26,346 --> 00:17:29,414
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It would have been a great gift
to know the outcome of this war.</b></font>

220
00:17:29,416 --> 00:17:33,851
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The gods can be frustrating
sometimes, lord cotys.</b></font>

221
00:17:39,692 --> 00:17:45,430
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>With respect, I fear tha t the task
ahead might not be suitable for a woman,</b></font>

222
00:17:45,432 --> 00:17:48,566
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>even if she is
an Amazon warrior.</b></font>

223
00:17:54,873 --> 00:17:57,208
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I stand corrected.</b></font>

224
00:17:59,245 --> 00:18:02,213
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>When the kings of
yesteryear built this citadel,</b></font>

225
00:18:02,215 --> 00:18:06,184
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>it was intended as
the high seat of all thrace.</b></font>

226
00:18:06,186 --> 00:18:09,153
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But now thrace is divided.</b></font>

227
00:18:09,155 --> 00:18:10,388
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This war has
depleted our forces.</b></font>

228
00:18:10,390 --> 00:18:14,559
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We're left with nothing but farmers
and merchants to replenish our army.</b></font>

229
00:18:14,561 --> 00:18:16,894
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It takes every one of us
to resist rhesus.</b></font>

230
00:18:16,896 --> 00:18:21,265
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>People think that he cannot be
killed by an ordinary mortal.</b></font>

231
00:18:21,366 --> 00:18:23,401
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Only by a God.</b></font>

232
00:18:24,069 --> 00:18:25,636
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Rhesus is a sorcerer.</b></font>

233
00:18:25,638 --> 00:18:28,973
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>His magic words confuse men,
bend them to his will.</i></b></font>

234
00:18:28,975 --> 00:18:33,811
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>He leads an army of monsters,
half horse, half human.</i></b></font>

235
00:18:35,314 --> 00:18:36,547
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Centaurs?</b></font>

236
00:18:36,549 --> 00:18:39,984
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- You've actually seen them?
- They have been seen.</b></font>

237
00:18:42,521 --> 00:18:43,688
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Come, Hercules.</b></font>

238
00:18:43,690 --> 00:18:48,192
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Let me show you what misery
rhesus has brought us.</b></font>

239
00:18:50,863 --> 00:18:54,799
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Every week, more refugees
arrive seeking my protection,</b></font>

240
00:18:54,801 --> 00:19:00,071
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>most of them covered in blood,
crippled or burnt by rhesus' men.</b></font>

241
00:19:00,073 --> 00:19:05,309
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I feared nothing could ever be
good again, till you arrived.</b></font>

242
00:19:05,544 --> 00:19:08,312
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm just
a mercenary fighting for gold.</b></font>

243
00:19:08,881 --> 00:19:12,750
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>How we view ourselves
is of little consequence.</b></font>

244
00:19:12,752 --> 00:19:15,720
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>How others
perceive us is important.</b></font>

245
00:19:15,722 --> 00:19:18,589
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And your name, like it or not,</b></font>

246
00:19:18,591 --> 00:19:21,292
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>is a rallying cry.</b></font>

247
00:19:26,031 --> 00:19:31,135
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I have seen too much reality to
trust in legends, and I am not alone.</b></font>

248
00:19:31,403 --> 00:19:34,071
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Nobody has any faith anymore.</b></font>

249
00:19:34,073 --> 00:19:39,777
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The people need a hero. They
need someone to look up to.</b></font>

250
00:19:40,212 --> 00:19:44,148
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My son believes in you.</b></font>

251
00:19:44,650 --> 00:19:46,584
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Bring us peace,</b></font>

252
00:19:47,653 --> 00:19:50,755
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and I will
believe in you, too.</b></font>

253
00:19:58,797 --> 00:20:00,031
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm convinced
these are good people.</b></font>

254
00:20:00,033 --> 00:20:03,734
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I see. And who's more
convincing, cotys or his daughter?</b></font>

255
00:20:03,736 --> 00:20:07,672
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>All the gold on earth is not as
convincing as a pair of breasts.</b></font>

256
00:20:07,674 --> 00:20:09,407
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Maybe, but gold never ages.</b></font>

257
00:20:09,409 --> 00:20:12,076
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Which is why I got them
to double our price.</b></font>

258
00:20:12,078 --> 00:20:15,980
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Double your weight in gold?
Well done.</b></font>

259
00:20:15,982 --> 00:20:16,847
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Amphiaraus?</b></font>

260
00:20:16,849 --> 00:20:17,949
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>If it be the will of Zeus.</b></font>

261
00:20:17,951 --> 00:20:19,951
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Which title sounds more
terrifying to our enemies?</b></font>

262
00:20:19,953 --> 00:20:24,322
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Savior of thrace"
or " A legend is born"?</b></font>

263
00:20:24,324 --> 00:20:26,724
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Both sound
terrifyingly boring.</b></font>

264
00:20:27,393 --> 00:20:30,828
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What are we supposed to do
with an army of farmers?</b></font>

265
00:20:33,599 --> 00:20:34,565
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Train them.</b></font>

266
00:20:34,567 --> 00:20:37,535
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Oh, shit.</b></font>

267
00:20:42,908 --> 00:20:47,511
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>In war, there is one thing
more important than killing.</b></font>

268
00:20:47,679 --> 00:20:48,913
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Surviving.</b></font>

269
00:20:48,915 --> 00:20:53,784
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My companions and I will
show you how to stay alive,</b></font>

270
00:20:53,786 --> 00:20:58,155
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>so that you may return home
to your farms someday.</b></font>

271
00:21:00,592 --> 00:21:01,959
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Autolycus.</b></font>

272
00:21:02,261 --> 00:21:04,695
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Shield wall! Form!</b></font>

273
00:21:22,282 --> 00:21:24,849
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Corpses!
Every last one of you!</b></font>

274
00:21:24,851 --> 00:21:28,085
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Because your
shield wall was weak.</b></font>

275
00:21:28,287 --> 00:21:29,587
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Dead.</b></font>

276
00:21:29,988 --> 00:21:31,389
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Dead.</b></font>

277
00:21:31,690 --> 00:21:33,190
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Very dead.</b></font>

278
00:21:34,726 --> 00:21:36,193
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Soldier,</b></font>

279
00:21:36,195 --> 00:21:38,329
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>many lives depend on you.</b></font>

280
00:21:38,331 --> 00:21:41,766
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>When attacked,
lock your feet in the ground.</b></font>

281
00:21:44,269 --> 00:21:45,770
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You understand?</b></font>

282
00:21:45,772 --> 00:21:47,238
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Yes, sir.</b></font>

283
00:21:47,506 --> 00:21:49,774
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>When a shield wall is strong,</b></font>

284
00:21:50,008 --> 00:21:52,677
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>nothing can ever defeat it!</b></font>

285
00:21:52,679 --> 00:21:55,913
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You must learn to work
together, react together.</b></font>

286
00:21:55,915 --> 00:22:00,217
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>When you do, each individual
will become a link in a chain</b></font>

287
00:22:00,219 --> 00:22:03,354
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>that will be
stronger than iron.</b></font>

288
00:22:07,326 --> 00:22:09,994
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I hope the enemy
has a sense of humor.</b></font>

289
00:22:10,495 --> 00:22:15,199
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Right. Today's lesson,
how not to stab yourselves!</b></font>

290
00:22:15,267 --> 00:22:20,905
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It is imperative that we strike
now, my lord, given this opportunity.</b></font>

291
00:22:20,907 --> 00:22:22,540
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Ah! There you are!</b></font>

292
00:22:22,542 --> 00:22:27,478
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules, my scouts have brought
news. Rhesus is on the move.</b></font>

293
00:22:27,480 --> 00:22:29,647
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Archers who shoot lightning
from their bows.</b></font>

294
00:22:29,649 --> 00:22:33,617
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And infantry 4,000-strong,
their minds bewitched.</b></font>

295
00:22:33,619 --> 00:22:35,186
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Demons march with them.</b></font>

296
00:22:35,188 --> 00:22:36,854
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>So now we're fighting demons.</b></font>

297
00:22:36,856 --> 00:22:40,257
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No stranger than the monsters
I hear you faced, Hercules.</b></font>

298
00:22:40,259 --> 00:22:44,128
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My lord, rhesus is preparing
to attack bessi lands.</b></font>

299
00:22:44,130 --> 00:22:45,930
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He will be on
them within six days.</b></font>

300
00:22:45,932 --> 00:22:49,100
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>If the bessi fall, we're next.
Unless we intercept him.</b></font>

301
00:22:49,102 --> 00:22:53,137
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Your men need weeks, if not months,
of training before they're ready.</b></font>

302
00:22:53,139 --> 00:22:56,540
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The bessi are a fierce
but primitive tribe.</b></font>

303
00:22:56,542 --> 00:23:00,211
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>If we do not protect them,
then there will be a bloodbath.</b></font>

304
00:23:00,213 --> 00:23:01,746
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Face rhesus with
an untrained army</b></font>

305
00:23:01,748 --> 00:23:03,781
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and you risk losing
far more than a single battle.</b></font>

306
00:23:03,783 --> 00:23:08,953
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My lord, rhesus is coming.
I vouch my life on it.</b></font>

307
00:23:09,521 --> 00:23:10,721
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The longer rhesus lives,</b></font>

308
00:23:10,723 --> 00:23:16,660
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>the more villages will be burnt and
the more innocents will be killed.</b></font>

309
00:23:16,662 --> 00:23:20,698
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Assemble your men.
We march tomorrow.</b></font>

310
00:23:22,033 --> 00:23:26,804
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules, the gods
have offered us a gift.</b></font>

311
00:23:26,806 --> 00:23:28,606
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We must not squander it.</b></font>

312
00:23:28,608 --> 00:23:31,776
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Are your gods going to
be fighting with us?</b></font>

313
00:23:32,177 --> 00:23:33,411
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No.</b></font>

314
00:23:33,745 --> 00:23:36,247
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The son of Zeus will.</b></font>

315
00:23:50,128 --> 00:23:53,998
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I've seen how you
watch over Hercules.</b></font>

316
00:23:56,268 --> 00:23:58,402
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Tell me,</b></font>

317
00:23:58,404 --> 00:24:01,205
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>how did a woman,</b></font>

318
00:24:01,207 --> 00:24:03,574
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>beautiful woman,</b></font>

319
00:24:03,576 --> 00:24:07,278
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>fall in with
these hardened men?</b></font>

320
00:24:07,280 --> 00:24:08,679
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Killers?</b></font>

321
00:24:12,784 --> 00:24:15,686
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Son of Zeus need
a woman's protection?</b></font>

322
00:24:15,688 --> 00:24:17,988
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I don't protect him.</b></font>

323
00:24:19,191 --> 00:24:21,559
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I protect you from him.</b></font>

324
00:24:23,128 --> 00:24:24,395
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hmm.</b></font>

325
00:24:44,216 --> 00:24:48,586
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>General, from now on, maybe you
should favor the company of your men.</b></font>

326
00:24:56,595 --> 00:24:57,661
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He pulled a knife?</b></font>

327
00:24:57,663 --> 00:25:00,731
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It was only a small prick.</b></font>

328
00:25:34,533 --> 00:25:37,535
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Ah!</b></font>

329
00:25:41,007 --> 00:25:44,041
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Your mother told you to
stay away. You should listen.</b></font>

330
00:25:44,543 --> 00:25:46,410
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What's wrong with him?</b></font>

331
00:25:49,414 --> 00:25:52,349
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Tydeus is my
most loyal warrior.</b></font>

332
00:25:53,385 --> 00:25:54,785
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He was born in war.</b></font>

333
00:25:54,787 --> 00:25:59,623
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>When I found him,
he was more animal than human.</b></font>

334
00:26:02,727 --> 00:26:05,563
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He never speaks
of what he saw.</b></font>

335
00:26:05,931 --> 00:26:08,165
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He never speaks at all.</b></font>

336
00:26:08,600 --> 00:26:11,835
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But he relives it every night.</b></font>

337
00:26:13,438 --> 00:26:14,405
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Come.</b></font>

338
00:26:14,407 --> 00:26:16,307
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Let's find your mother.</b></font>

339
00:26:21,780 --> 00:26:25,182
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Arius: When I grow up, I want
to be a great hero like you.</b></font>

340
00:26:25,184 --> 00:26:28,786
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Like me?
- No hero is greater than Hercules.</b></font>

341
00:26:28,788 --> 00:26:29,353
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I know all your labors.</b></font>

342
00:26:29,355 --> 00:26:33,824
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Like the cretan bull, you wrestled
it for seven days and seven nights.</b></font>

343
00:26:33,826 --> 00:26:34,525
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Uh, that's a bit exaggerated.</b></font>

344
00:26:34,527 --> 00:26:38,362
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- And struck it 49 times with your club.
- Maybe not quite that many.</b></font>

345
00:26:38,364 --> 00:26:43,133
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Until it fell dead and crete was
saved. It's my favorite labor.</b></font>

346
00:26:43,135 --> 00:26:44,535
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Also queen hippolyta's belt,</b></font>

347
00:26:44,537 --> 00:26:48,772
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>with its buxom Amazons
and exciting bondage.</b></font>

348
00:26:48,907 --> 00:26:52,643
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Do you even know what that means?
- No.</b></font>

349
00:27:01,886 --> 00:27:04,088
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Mother.
- Arius.</b></font>

350
00:27:04,090 --> 00:27:06,857
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're supposed to be in bed.</b></font>

351
00:27:08,593 --> 00:27:10,361
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Why are you in the hospice?</b></font>

352
00:27:10,363 --> 00:27:12,930
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My mother saves
people's lives.</b></font>

353
00:27:12,932 --> 00:27:14,732
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Many of our physicians
were killed during battle.</b></font>

354
00:27:14,734 --> 00:27:19,236
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>So, out of necessity, I taught
myself the art of healing.</b></font>

355
00:27:20,438 --> 00:27:21,005
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>If I could be like you,</b></font>

356
00:27:21,007 --> 00:27:25,175
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I would protect all of thrace
and no one would ever get hurt.</b></font>

357
00:27:34,919 --> 00:27:36,387
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Here.</b></font>

358
00:27:37,055 --> 00:27:40,557
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I was going to give this
to someone else,</b></font>

359
00:27:41,359 --> 00:27:44,028
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>but I never got the chance.</b></font>

360
00:27:45,063 --> 00:27:47,264
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Only a hero may wear this.</b></font>

361
00:27:47,266 --> 00:27:50,801
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But to become a hero,
you must grow strong.</b></font>

362
00:27:53,672 --> 00:27:55,706
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Is this
the nemean lion's tooth?</b></font>

363
00:27:55,708 --> 00:27:58,509
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- It is.
- Thank you.</b></font>

364
00:27:59,277 --> 00:28:00,411
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Thank you.</b></font>

365
00:28:00,413 --> 00:28:01,779
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Good night.</b></font>

366
00:28:02,113 --> 00:28:04,281
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Good night, Hercules.</b></font>

367
00:28:07,619 --> 00:28:09,553
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Have no fear.</b></font>

368
00:28:09,555 --> 00:28:15,159
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>If you fall in the service of a just
cause, your souls will go to elysium,</b></font>

369
00:28:15,161 --> 00:28:20,264
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>where they will dwell forever
among the shades of heroes,</b></font>

370
00:28:20,266 --> 00:28:21,732
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>like theseus.</b></font>

371
00:28:21,734 --> 00:28:22,866
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Odysseus!</b></font>

372
00:28:22,868 --> 00:28:24,001
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And the great achilles.</b></font>

373
00:28:24,003 --> 00:28:29,373
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Or if you're lucky, you'll go to
Hades, where all the fun people are.</b></font>

374
00:28:37,182 --> 00:28:38,182
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Iolaus.</b></font>

375
00:28:38,184 --> 00:28:39,850
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Your place is beside lord
cotys, where it's safe.</b></font>

376
00:28:39,852 --> 00:28:43,821
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I've been giving it a lot of thought,
and I really feel I'm ready to fight.</b></font>

377
00:28:43,823 --> 00:28:45,723
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're a storyteller,
not a warrior.</b></font>

378
00:28:45,725 --> 00:28:46,657
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We share the same blood.</b></font>

379
00:28:46,659 --> 00:28:49,827
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And I will not see it shed.
Chariot.</b></font>

380
00:28:49,994 --> 00:28:51,161
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Now.</b></font>

381
00:28:59,037 --> 00:29:00,237
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Thracians,</b></font>

382
00:29:00,239 --> 00:29:03,874
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>the shield wall is your home.
Your shelter.</b></font>

383
00:29:03,876 --> 00:29:07,878
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>When you sleep,
the wall is your blanket.</b></font>

384
00:29:07,880 --> 00:29:11,515
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>When you fight,
the wall is your armor.</b></font>

385
00:29:11,517 --> 00:29:13,817
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The shield wall will
never break formation</b></font>

386
00:29:13,819 --> 00:29:17,588
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>as long as there is
breath in your body.</b></font>

387
00:29:17,789 --> 00:29:20,290
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Remember these words,</b></font>

388
00:29:20,825 --> 00:29:23,293
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>and you will taste victory.</b></font>

389
00:29:23,995 --> 00:29:26,730
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Move the army out!
- Soldier 1: Move out!</b></font>

390
00:30:34,599 --> 00:30:35,833
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Halt!</b></font>

391
00:30:36,367 --> 00:30:37,100
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Halt!</b></font>

392
00:30:37,102 --> 00:30:39,970
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Halt!
- Soldier 2: Halt!</b></font>

393
00:31:11,236 --> 00:31:12,836
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We are too late.</b></font>

394
00:31:12,838 --> 00:31:16,106
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Rhesus has already been here.</b></font>

395
00:31:18,977 --> 00:31:22,880
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Leave the chariots.
We'll go down on foot.</b></font>

396
00:31:50,675 --> 00:31:54,411
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The lion and crow
cross a field of corpses.</b></font>

397
00:31:55,580 --> 00:31:58,482
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I hate being
right all the time.</b></font>

398
00:32:03,855 --> 00:32:04,454
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Halt.</b></font>

399
00:32:04,456 --> 00:32:06,723
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Halt!
- Soldier 1: Halt!</b></font>

400
00:32:17,268 --> 00:32:19,069
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This head is rotting.</b></font>

401
00:32:20,905 --> 00:32:22,739
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>A week old, at least.</b></font>

402
00:32:25,076 --> 00:32:28,478
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Yet some of these
bodies are fresh.</b></font>

403
00:32:42,962 --> 00:32:44,728
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Uncle!</b></font>

404
00:32:53,171 --> 00:32:56,940
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And we've walked into a trap.</b></font>

405
00:33:02,847 --> 00:33:07,250
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Shield wall! Form a single square!
Protect lord cotys! Iolaus, go!</b></font>

406
00:33:07,252 --> 00:33:09,286
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Shield wall!</b></font>

407
00:33:17,795 --> 00:33:21,031
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We're here to help them.
Why are they attacking?</b></font>

408
00:33:21,033 --> 00:33:21,999
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This is rhesus' doing.</b></font>

409
00:33:22,001 --> 00:33:25,002
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>They say his spells have
the power to cloud minds.</b></font>

410
00:33:25,004 --> 00:33:28,271
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Turn comrades
against each other.</b></font>

411
00:33:35,646 --> 00:33:38,515
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>King's guards,
around lord cotys!</b></font>

412
00:33:46,858 --> 00:33:49,526
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Amphiaraus,
do we die in this battle?</b></font>

413
00:33:49,528 --> 00:33:54,231
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My time's not come yet.
Not sure about yours.</b></font>

414
00:33:55,600 --> 00:33:57,834
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>That's comforting.</b></font>

415
00:34:05,043 --> 00:34:07,444
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I think he wants a challenge.</b></font>

416
00:34:25,997 --> 00:34:30,901
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules' fists have been
dipped in the blood of the hydra!</b></font>

417
00:34:30,903 --> 00:34:33,537
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Lethal to anyone but him!</b></font>

418
00:34:36,174 --> 00:34:37,441
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Watch!</b></font>

419
00:34:49,254 --> 00:34:50,420
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Did you see that?</b></font>

420
00:34:50,422 --> 00:34:52,389
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The gods fight on our side!</b></font>

421
00:34:54,560 --> 00:34:57,260
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules! Hercules! Hercules!</b></font>

422
00:34:57,262 --> 00:35:00,630
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules! Hercules! Hercules!</b></font>

423
00:35:00,632 --> 00:35:02,299
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules! Hercules!</b></font>

424
00:35:02,301 --> 00:35:05,669
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules! Hercules! Hercules!</b></font>

425
00:35:19,484 --> 00:35:21,418
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Battle position!</b></font>

426
00:35:29,494 --> 00:35:33,830
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Lady Artemis, if I am to fall,
let me be judged...</b></font>

427
00:36:07,298 --> 00:36:09,166
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Stand fast!</b></font>

428
00:36:23,915 --> 00:36:26,383
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hold your position!</b></font>

429
00:36:41,766 --> 00:36:43,600
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Do not yield!</b></font>

430
00:37:39,357 --> 00:37:42,926
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No retreat! Stay in the wall!</b></font>

431
00:37:43,694 --> 00:37:45,795
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hold the lines!</b></font>

432
00:37:45,930 --> 00:37:47,097
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Do not yield!</b></font>

433
00:37:47,099 --> 00:37:50,200
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Defend lord cotys!</b></font>

434
00:38:16,260 --> 00:38:18,561
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The wall has been breached!</b></font>

435
00:38:20,765 --> 00:38:25,935
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Seal up the shield wall!
Defend lord cotys!</b></font>

436
00:38:31,976 --> 00:38:33,410
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Whip!</b></font>

437
00:38:43,487 --> 00:38:45,322
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules!</b></font>

438
00:38:45,589 --> 00:38:47,290
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Bring the chariots!</b></font>

439
00:38:54,465 --> 00:38:56,900
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Sitacles: Defend your lord!</b></font>

440
00:39:07,511 --> 00:39:09,946
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No!</b></font>

441
00:40:25,489 --> 00:40:26,956
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Advance!</b></font>

442
00:40:26,958 --> 00:40:28,892
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Advance!</b></font>

443
00:40:46,777 --> 00:40:48,311
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Make way!</b></font>

444
00:40:59,757 --> 00:41:02,292
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Where is rhesus?</b></font>

445
00:41:22,980 --> 00:41:24,681
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Lord cotys.</b></font>

446
00:41:25,216 --> 00:41:28,017
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We came here to
save this village,</b></font>

447
00:41:28,019 --> 00:41:31,621
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>but, no, they killed
half my army.</b></font>

448
00:41:32,556 --> 00:41:33,957
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Rhesus.</b></font>

449
00:41:34,191 --> 00:41:36,059
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This is all his doing.</b></font>

450
00:41:36,061 --> 00:41:37,560
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And yours.</b></font>

451
00:41:37,661 --> 00:41:38,094
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I warned you.</b></font>

452
00:41:38,096 --> 00:41:41,598
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Your men are brave, but
untrained, unprepared for battle.</b></font>

453
00:41:41,600 --> 00:41:44,634
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Give me time to make warriors.</b></font>

454
00:41:47,438 --> 00:41:48,838
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Very well.</b></font>

455
00:41:51,208 --> 00:41:57,347
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Cover up, before your loyal army
sees you bleed like a mortal.</b></font>

456
00:42:06,891 --> 00:42:08,157
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Phineas.</b></font>

457
00:42:08,159 --> 00:42:10,226
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You plead your life.</b></font>

458
00:42:10,228 --> 00:42:12,595
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And I gladly offer it.</b></font>

459
00:42:13,931 --> 00:42:15,832
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I failed to see this trap.</b></font>

460
00:42:15,834 --> 00:42:17,934
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The fault is mine!
Spare the other scouts.</b></font>

461
00:42:17,936 --> 00:42:19,969
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>General sitacles.</b></font>

462
00:42:19,971 --> 00:42:23,840
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I think we've lost enough men
for the day, don't you?</b></font>

463
00:42:23,842 --> 00:42:25,808
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But just to avoid
future misunderstandings,</b></font>

464
00:42:25,810 --> 00:42:30,280
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'll be taking charge
of your scouts from now on.</b></font>

465
00:42:30,282 --> 00:42:32,248
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Is that clear?</b></font>

466
00:42:37,388 --> 00:42:38,888
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Thank you.</b></font>

467
00:42:38,890 --> 00:42:42,392
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Another mistake,
I'll end you myself.</b></font>

468
00:43:12,056 --> 00:43:16,759
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm applying a salve of mint,
chamomile and Clay to seal the wound.</b></font>

469
00:43:16,761 --> 00:43:20,730
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This is extract of lithops for
the pain, a powerful sedative.</b></font>

470
00:43:20,732 --> 00:43:25,401
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It should rest you after consuming
it. It may have certain side effects.</b></font>

471
00:43:25,403 --> 00:43:26,736
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I don't need it.</b></font>

472
00:43:26,738 --> 00:43:30,173
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Ah, forgive me, I forgot.
No mortal can harm Hercules.</b></font>

473
00:43:30,175 --> 00:43:35,445
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And, uh, your lion's hide
is indestructible?</b></font>

474
00:43:36,447 --> 00:43:39,248
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Drink, son of Zeus.</b></font>

475
00:43:41,218 --> 00:43:45,788
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Arius' father was the same,
he distrusted medicines.</b></font>

476
00:43:45,790 --> 00:43:47,156
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Where is he now?</b></font>

477
00:43:47,424 --> 00:43:51,127
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Taken by the gods
before my son was born.</b></font>

478
00:43:51,129 --> 00:43:52,595
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm sorry.</b></font>

479
00:43:53,130 --> 00:43:54,897
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I never knew my father.</b></font>

480
00:43:55,499 --> 00:44:00,370
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well, he must have been
very, very strong.</b></font>

481
00:44:02,806 --> 00:44:04,440
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Tell me about arius.</b></font>

482
00:44:04,442 --> 00:44:07,176
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Oh. He's a good boy.</b></font>

483
00:44:07,178 --> 00:44:10,680
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And someday,
he will make a fine king.</b></font>

484
00:44:10,748 --> 00:44:12,382
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Do you have any children?</b></font>

485
00:44:16,220 --> 00:44:17,787
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Do they live in Athens?</b></font>

486
00:44:17,789 --> 00:44:20,256
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Thank you for your care.</b></font>

487
00:44:30,234 --> 00:44:32,669
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The sedative
will help you rest.</b></font>

488
00:45:04,601 --> 00:45:07,937
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>How could you do
such a terrible thing?</b></font>

489
00:45:07,939 --> 00:45:08,871
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>By law, I should execute you,</b></font>

490
00:45:08,873 --> 00:45:12,942
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>but I believe a more fitting
punishment would be to let you live.</b></font>

491
00:45:12,944 --> 00:45:16,612
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>So you can walk the earth in
torment, haunted by the knowledge</b></font>

492
00:45:16,614 --> 00:45:21,884
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>that you alone are responsible
for the death of your loved ones.</b></font>

493
00:45:23,120 --> 00:45:25,354
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The great Hercules.</b></font>

494
00:45:25,589 --> 00:45:30,526
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hands forever stained
with innocent blood.</b></font>

495
00:45:30,627 --> 00:45:33,663
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Get out, you monster.</b></font>

496
00:45:33,665 --> 00:45:34,697
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Get out!</b></font>

497
00:46:46,904 --> 00:46:48,805
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No!</b></font>

498
00:47:27,544 --> 00:47:31,314
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It happened
again, didn't it, hmm?</b></font>

499
00:47:31,316 --> 00:47:35,351
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Another vision of Cerberus,
the three-headed beast of Hades?</b></font>

500
00:47:35,353 --> 00:47:39,222
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The gods show you things
they don't share with others.</b></font>

501
00:47:39,224 --> 00:47:42,758
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>There's a word for that.
Madness.</b></font>

502
00:47:42,760 --> 00:47:44,727
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>When we were
driven from Athens,</b></font>

503
00:47:44,729 --> 00:47:47,663
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I consulted the oracle
of delphi on your behalf.</b></font>

504
00:47:47,665 --> 00:47:49,532
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Do you remember her prophecy?</b></font>

505
00:47:49,534 --> 00:47:53,970
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>"Hercules must finish the
labor that remains unfinished."</b></font>

506
00:47:53,972 --> 00:47:56,138
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And what is that, Hercules?</b></font>

507
00:47:56,140 --> 00:48:00,910
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Confront the beast that haunts
you. Only then will you find peace.</b></font>

508
00:48:00,912 --> 00:48:01,477
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I speak from experience.</b></font>

509
00:48:01,479 --> 00:48:06,549
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No matter how far you run, no matter
how fast you go, the beast will follow.</b></font>

510
00:48:06,551 --> 00:48:09,986
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Man cannot escape his fate.</b></font>

511
00:48:24,701 --> 00:48:27,336
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Room for one more
in your company?</b></font>

512
00:48:27,338 --> 00:48:31,641
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It'd be a pleasure having female
companionship for a change.</b></font>

513
00:48:31,643 --> 00:48:34,577
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Atalanta doesn't quite count.
No offense.</b></font>

514
00:48:34,579 --> 00:48:37,847
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>If only your manhood
was as long as your tongue.</b></font>

515
00:48:37,981 --> 00:48:40,616
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Both can satisfy
in different ways.</b></font>

516
00:48:43,086 --> 00:48:47,890
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're a famed storyteller,
iolaus. Grace me with a story.</b></font>

517
00:48:47,892 --> 00:48:50,793
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Any particular subject,
my lady?</b></font>

518
00:48:50,894 --> 00:48:54,830
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Murder, of a woman
and her three children.</b></font>

519
00:48:56,366 --> 00:49:00,036
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Is it true? Did Hercules
slaughter his own family?</b></font>

520
00:49:00,038 --> 00:49:03,039
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Who said so?
- Oh, soldiers talk.</b></font>

521
00:49:03,041 --> 00:49:05,841
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>They say if Hercules
ever returns to Athens,</b></font>

522
00:49:05,843 --> 00:49:08,611
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>king eurystheus
will have him executed.</b></font>

523
00:49:12,449 --> 00:49:16,419
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules had completed his labors
and returned home. But hera...</b></font>

524
00:49:16,421 --> 00:49:19,322
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No myths. I want the truth.</b></font>

525
00:49:19,324 --> 00:49:21,490
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No one knows the truth.</b></font>

526
00:49:22,392 --> 00:49:23,192
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Not for sure.</b></font>

527
00:49:23,194 --> 00:49:29,031
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We found Hercules alone. His wife,
megara and the children, dead.</b></font>

528
00:49:29,033 --> 00:49:30,833
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He remembers nothing.</b></font>

529
00:49:30,835 --> 00:49:32,668
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Do you believe he is innocent?</b></font>

530
00:49:32,670 --> 00:49:38,441
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We grew up together, both orphans, trying
to survive in the streets of Athens.</b></font>

531
00:49:38,443 --> 00:49:43,179
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We found a home in the army.
Looked out for each other.</b></font>

532
00:49:43,313 --> 00:49:47,483
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules'
strength set him apart.</b></font>

533
00:49:47,485 --> 00:49:51,620
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Kings of Athens started to send him
on all the most dangerous missions.</b></font>

534
00:49:51,622 --> 00:49:53,089
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The twelve labors.</b></font>

535
00:49:53,091 --> 00:49:55,191
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And he took me with him.</b></font>

536
00:49:55,592 --> 00:49:56,659
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>To fight by his side.</b></font>

537
00:49:56,661 --> 00:49:59,628
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And with each mission,
our numbers grew.</b></font>

538
00:49:59,630 --> 00:50:04,266
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Scythia, the Amazon kingdom where the
royal family had been assassinated.</b></font>

539
00:50:04,268 --> 00:50:07,203
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My family was gone.
Everyone was gone.</b></font>

540
00:50:07,205 --> 00:50:10,272
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules helped me
avenge their murder.</b></font>

541
00:50:10,274 --> 00:50:12,541
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He became my brother-in-arms.</b></font>

542
00:50:12,909 --> 00:50:16,112
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Thebes, the city of corpses,</b></font>

543
00:50:16,114 --> 00:50:18,647
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>where we found a single child,</b></font>

544
00:50:19,116 --> 00:50:20,883
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>still alive.</b></font>

545
00:50:20,885 --> 00:50:22,518
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules took tydeus in when</b></font>

546
00:50:22,520 --> 00:50:26,255
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>everyone else saw
nothing but a wild animal.</b></font>

547
00:50:26,790 --> 00:50:30,126
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You know how a rumor spreads.
How a legend grows.</b></font>

548
00:50:30,128 --> 00:50:31,927
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules' deeds
were so incredible,</b></font>

549
00:50:31,929 --> 00:50:36,499
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>they could not possibly have
been performed by a mere mortal.</b></font>

550
00:50:36,566 --> 00:50:37,767
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>So we played along.</b></font>

551
00:50:37,769 --> 00:50:43,406
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We encourage people to think Hercules
was the son of Zeus. It's good.</b></font>

552
00:50:43,408 --> 00:50:45,207
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Scares the enemy.</b></font>

553
00:50:45,342 --> 00:50:47,343
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Iolaus helps.</b></font>

554
00:50:47,345 --> 00:50:48,844
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He talks nice.</b></font>

555
00:50:50,013 --> 00:50:52,748
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're very loyal friends.</b></font>

556
00:50:52,750 --> 00:50:54,683
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're avoiding my question.</b></font>

557
00:50:56,019 --> 00:50:57,119
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules is a warrior.</b></font>

558
00:50:57,121 --> 00:50:59,255
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And there is something
that haunts warriors.</b></font>

559
00:50:59,257 --> 00:51:00,856
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It can cloud their minds.</b></font>

560
00:51:00,858 --> 00:51:04,360
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We call it the blood rage.</b></font>

561
00:51:04,461 --> 00:51:07,129
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This rage afflicted Hercules.</b></font>

562
00:51:07,131 --> 00:51:09,632
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He made me vow to keep
the world away from him.</b></font>

563
00:51:09,634 --> 00:51:13,135
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>To make sure that he would
never harm innocents again.</b></font>

564
00:51:13,137 --> 00:51:16,705
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And that,
my lady, is the truth.</b></font>

565
00:51:16,973 --> 00:51:18,574
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The truth,</b></font>

566
00:51:20,243 --> 00:51:22,344
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Whatever the truth,</b></font>

567
00:51:22,346 --> 00:51:25,314
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>the death of his loved ones
haunts Hercules.</b></font>

568
00:51:25,316 --> 00:51:28,284
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Only the gods can help him,</b></font>

569
00:51:29,152 --> 00:51:31,153
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>if he listens.</b></font>

570
00:51:36,760 --> 00:51:40,362
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Come! Gather around, soldiers
of thrace, and behold,</b></font>

571
00:51:40,364 --> 00:51:44,266
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>when Hercules gives an order,
even the gods listen.</b></font>

572
00:51:44,401 --> 00:51:46,168
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Zeus' master ironsmith,</b></font>

573
00:51:46,170 --> 00:51:48,003
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>using the forges
of your own citadel,</b></font>

574
00:51:48,005 --> 00:51:53,275
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>has crafted these divine weapons
that will make you invincible.</b></font>

575
00:51:53,277 --> 00:51:55,978
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>As steel is hewn into shields,</b></font>

576
00:51:55,980 --> 00:51:59,982
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>so, too, will you be
hewn into warriors.</b></font>

577
00:52:01,651 --> 00:52:05,955
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You shall carry
the shield of Hercules!</b></font>

578
00:52:13,964 --> 00:52:14,763
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It's lighter.</b></font>

579
00:52:14,765 --> 00:52:18,067
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Infused with the souls
of stymphalian birds</b></font>

580
00:52:18,069 --> 00:52:19,568
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>from Hercules' sixth labor!</b></font>

581
00:52:19,570 --> 00:52:23,939
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Spirits of birds?
How does that work, exactly?</b></font>

582
00:52:24,474 --> 00:52:26,208
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well, much as
birds take flight,</b></font>

583
00:52:26,210 --> 00:52:31,480
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>so, too, are these shields lighter
than air. It's in the fibers. Here.</b></font>

584
00:52:31,915 --> 00:52:34,950
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Try on the helmet of Hercules.</b></font>

585
00:52:41,358 --> 00:52:41,924
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It covers my whole face.</b></font>

586
00:52:41,926 --> 00:52:46,662
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Forged after Hercules' very own helmet,
when he defeated the demon geryon.</b></font>

587
00:52:46,664 --> 00:52:51,634
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You sure it wasn't your horseshit
that frightened geryon to death?</b></font>

588
00:52:52,102 --> 00:52:52,835
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Mmm?</b></font>

589
00:52:52,837 --> 00:52:53,969
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Io General sitacles,</b></font>

590
00:52:53,971 --> 00:52:58,340
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>perhaps you would care to
inspect the armor of Hercules?</b></font>

591
00:53:13,490 --> 00:53:15,691
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Leather armor?</b></font>

592
00:53:15,926 --> 00:53:17,159
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Mmm?</b></font>

593
00:53:17,161 --> 00:53:19,495
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We will be skewered like pigs.</b></font>

594
00:53:23,433 --> 00:53:25,100
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Linothorax.</b></font>

595
00:53:25,468 --> 00:53:29,138
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hewn from the skin of
the erymanthean boar.</b></font>

596
00:53:29,140 --> 00:53:31,440
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It's indestructible.</b></font>

597
00:53:32,442 --> 00:53:37,213
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Wait. If it's indestructible, how
did Hercules cut it off the boar?</b></font>

598
00:53:37,948 --> 00:53:42,384
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He used
an indestructible blade.</b></font>

599
00:54:01,605 --> 00:54:04,139
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Soldiers: One, two.</b></font>

600
00:54:11,748 --> 00:54:13,349
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Get up.</b></font>

601
00:54:14,451 --> 00:54:15,684
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Next!</b></font>

602
00:54:23,426 --> 00:54:25,027
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Again!</b></font>

603
00:54:25,095 --> 00:54:26,795
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Both eyes open.</b></font>

604
00:54:28,598 --> 00:54:30,132
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Keep practicing.</b></font>

605
00:54:32,303 --> 00:54:34,136
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Firmer grip.</b></font>

606
00:54:34,537 --> 00:54:36,105
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Elbow up.</b></font>

607
00:54:37,474 --> 00:54:38,374
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Good.</b></font>

608
00:54:38,376 --> 00:54:40,442
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Shield wall! Form!</b></font>

609
00:54:45,115 --> 00:54:47,449
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Stand tall.</b></font>

610
00:54:50,020 --> 00:54:51,553
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Excellent.</b></font>

611
00:55:17,380 --> 00:55:20,149
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Careful you don't
cut yourself, boy.</b></font>

612
00:55:21,718 --> 00:55:23,218
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Again!</b></font>

613
00:55:30,026 --> 00:55:31,960
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Rhesus is here.</b></font>

614
00:55:31,962 --> 00:55:35,331
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Close enough to stick
a blade between his ribs.</b></font>

615
00:55:35,333 --> 00:55:35,898
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What did you see?</b></font>

616
00:55:35,900 --> 00:55:40,035
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Centaurs. Half man, half
horse. Hundreds of them.</b></font>

617
00:55:40,603 --> 00:55:41,937
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He saw shadows in the night.</b></font>

618
00:55:41,939 --> 00:55:44,873
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My lord, I will go ahead
into the rhesus camp.</b></font>

619
00:55:44,875 --> 00:55:48,077
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I will bring
word of his plans.</b></font>

620
00:55:51,281 --> 00:55:55,417
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>If we let them get past mount
asticus, thrace will fall.</b></font>

621
00:55:55,685 --> 00:55:56,719
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You want to stop rhesus?</b></font>

622
00:55:56,721 --> 00:55:58,954
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We'll go through the forest
and they'll never see us coming.</b></font>

623
00:55:58,956 --> 00:56:02,925
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It'll slow down our chariots.
A gamble.</b></font>

624
00:56:03,560 --> 00:56:04,927
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I have a plan.</b></font>

625
00:56:09,099 --> 00:56:10,065
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The scouts have returned.</b></font>

626
00:56:10,067 --> 00:56:14,236
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Rhesus has made his camp in
mount asticus, 72 leagues away.</b></font>

627
00:56:14,238 --> 00:56:17,373
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Once these men
are ready, we march.</b></font>

628
00:56:17,941 --> 00:56:21,377
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>So, have you seen
if we win or lose?</b></font>

629
00:56:21,379 --> 00:56:25,381
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The gods have been annoyingly
silent on that matter.</b></font>

630
00:56:25,383 --> 00:56:26,181
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What they have told me is that</b></font>

631
00:56:26,183 --> 00:56:30,386
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm soon to discover there
truly is a heaven or a hell.</b></font>

632
00:56:31,788 --> 00:56:32,654
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>When will you die?</b></font>

633
00:56:32,656 --> 00:56:36,525
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Within a week in a place that
looks an awful lot like hell.</b></font>

634
00:56:36,527 --> 00:56:40,696
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>As always, the gods
are generous with hints,</b></font>

635
00:56:40,698 --> 00:56:43,265
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>but cheap on specifics.</b></font>

636
00:56:45,402 --> 00:56:46,735
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Cheer up, Hercules.</b></font>

637
00:56:46,737 --> 00:56:51,640
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I've lived, not always well,
but long enough.</b></font>

638
00:56:52,976 --> 00:56:55,878
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm ready for what's next.</b></font>

639
00:57:01,351 --> 00:57:04,219
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Thracians, halt!</b></font>

640
00:57:05,322 --> 00:57:08,023
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Shield wall! Form!</b></font>

641
00:57:11,694 --> 00:57:13,429
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Battle positions!</b></font>

642
00:57:16,733 --> 00:57:18,300
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Tydeus?</b></font>

643
00:58:03,980 --> 00:58:05,814
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>There is no enemy camp.</b></font>

644
00:58:06,182 --> 00:58:08,750
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This is the right place.</b></font>

645
00:58:26,069 --> 00:58:27,769
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Centaurs!</b></font>

646
00:58:28,137 --> 00:58:29,838
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>They're real.</b></font>

647
00:58:53,162 --> 00:58:55,364
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It seems that we're expected.</b></font>

648
00:59:10,813 --> 00:59:12,314
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Centaurs?</b></font>

649
00:59:33,002 --> 00:59:33,302
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Rhesus!</b></font>

650
00:59:33,304 --> 00:59:38,874
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You have come looking for a
fight, and we are happy to oblige.</b></font>

651
00:59:39,609 --> 00:59:42,578
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules. The son of Zeus.</b></font>

652
00:59:42,679 --> 00:59:44,813
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Your legend ends here.</b></font>

653
00:59:44,815 --> 00:59:46,348
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Look at me.</b></font>

654
00:59:47,183 --> 00:59:48,817
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Do I look afraid?</b></font>

655
00:59:57,226 --> 00:59:58,660
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Phineas.</b></font>

656
00:59:59,629 --> 01:00:01,096
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Traitor!</b></font>

657
01:00:01,098 --> 01:00:03,231
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hades will have you!</b></font>

658
01:00:03,299 --> 01:00:05,901
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>After it has you, my lord.</b></font>

659
01:00:05,903 --> 01:00:07,102
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Rhesus: It is over, cotys.</b></font>

660
01:00:07,104 --> 01:00:11,406
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Mount asticus on your front.
The woods at your back.</b></font>

661
01:00:11,408 --> 01:00:14,109
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And my troops
outman you three to one.</b></font>

662
01:00:14,111 --> 01:00:18,880
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Surrender now, and we shall
consider being merciful.</b></font>

663
01:00:18,882 --> 01:00:22,484
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Men die who speak to my lord
in such a manner.</b></font>

664
01:00:28,591 --> 01:00:30,525
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You've made your choice.</b></font>

665
01:00:46,009 --> 01:00:47,242
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Go!</b></font>

666
01:00:58,321 --> 01:01:01,890
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>In this moment, on this day,</b></font>

667
01:01:01,892 --> 01:01:05,427
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>become the man
you were born to be!</b></font>

668
01:01:05,429 --> 01:01:10,899
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You have it within yourselves
to write your own legends!</b></font>

669
01:01:10,901 --> 01:01:15,337
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Let it be to death or victory!</b></font>

670
01:01:19,676 --> 01:01:21,043
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Charge!</b></font>

671
01:01:29,452 --> 01:01:30,952
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Shield wall!</b></font>

672
01:01:32,423 --> 01:01:33,889
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Flanks out!</b></font>

673
01:01:42,665 --> 01:01:44,599
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Maybe today.</b></font>

674
01:02:06,055 --> 01:02:07,355
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Now!</b></font>

675
01:02:25,541 --> 01:02:28,610
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Watch as the Amazon
uses the arrows of Artemis...</b></font>

676
01:02:28,612 --> 01:02:30,445
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Silence, boy!</b></font>

677
01:02:35,318 --> 01:02:36,852
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Spears forward!</b></font>

678
01:02:55,571 --> 01:02:57,472
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Archers, ready!</b></font>

679
01:02:58,508 --> 01:03:00,142
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Loose!</b></font>

680
01:03:51,594 --> 01:03:52,828
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Advance!</b></font>

681
01:04:01,704 --> 01:04:03,605
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Set them aflame!</b></font>

682
01:04:08,244 --> 01:04:09,778
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Take cover!</b></font>

683
01:04:10,079 --> 01:04:12,447
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Defend lord cotys!</b></font>

684
01:04:31,834 --> 01:04:33,201
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Maybe not.</b></font>

685
01:04:33,203 --> 01:04:35,370
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Shield wall! Attack!</b></font>

686
01:04:38,708 --> 01:04:40,475
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Push forward!</b></font>

687
01:04:53,356 --> 01:04:57,092
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>To kill a snake,
cut off its head.</b></font>

688
01:05:12,943 --> 01:05:16,077
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Victory is yours, lord cotys!</b></font>

689
01:05:16,079 --> 01:05:18,713
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It is not over yet!</b></font>

690
01:05:52,416 --> 01:05:54,416
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Fucking centaurs.</b></font>

691
01:05:59,423 --> 01:06:04,025
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>All: Hail, lord cotys! Hail, lord cotys!</b></font>

692
01:06:04,027 --> 01:06:08,530
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hail, lord cotys!
Hail, lord cotys!</b></font>

693
01:06:08,664 --> 01:06:11,166
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hail, lord cotys!</b></font>

694
01:06:38,160 --> 01:06:39,995
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Halt!</b></font>

695
01:06:46,737 --> 01:06:48,303
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Get up.</b></font>

696
01:06:49,138 --> 01:06:50,772
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Get up.</b></font>

697
01:06:57,647 --> 01:06:59,314
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Up.
- Enough!</b></font>

698
01:07:09,225 --> 01:07:12,460
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You helped
a tyrant enslave a nation.</b></font>

699
01:07:12,462 --> 01:07:15,663
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>All I did was stop you
from burning more villages.</b></font>

700
01:07:15,665 --> 01:07:17,599
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I burned no villages.</b></font>

701
01:07:17,767 --> 01:07:18,900
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Then who did?</b></font>

702
01:07:18,902 --> 01:07:20,769
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Ask yourself,
if cotys is beloved,</b></font>

703
01:07:20,771 --> 01:07:23,638
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>why did he need to hire
mercenaries to do his dirty work?</b></font>

704
01:07:23,640 --> 01:07:25,306
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Keep moving, dog.</b></font>

705
01:07:25,308 --> 01:07:28,943
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You've been
fighting on the wrong side.</b></font>

706
01:08:01,877 --> 01:08:03,411
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Where are you going?</b></font>

707
01:08:03,413 --> 01:08:06,247
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm taking some
water to the prisoner.</b></font>

708
01:08:08,250 --> 01:08:09,717
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Sit down.</b></font>

709
01:08:14,924 --> 01:08:16,791
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It's time.</b></font>

710
01:08:26,335 --> 01:08:29,904
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Thrace is finally united.</b></font>

711
01:08:31,841 --> 01:08:33,475
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>One land,</b></font>

712
01:08:33,943 --> 01:08:35,643
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>one king,</b></font>

713
01:08:36,779 --> 01:08:38,813
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>one thrace.</b></font>

714
01:08:39,448 --> 01:08:41,015
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>One land!</b></font>

715
01:08:41,017 --> 01:08:42,784
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>One king! One thrace!</b></font>

716
01:08:42,786 --> 01:08:46,654
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Thrace is not a man,
a king, or a God!</b></font>

717
01:08:46,656 --> 01:08:48,323
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Thrace is her people!</b></font>

718
01:08:54,997 --> 01:08:57,999
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Who cares what rhesus claims?
Our work is done.</b></font>

719
01:08:58,001 --> 01:09:00,301
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Let's collect our
fee and be gone.</b></font>

720
01:09:11,780 --> 01:09:13,715
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Don't do anything foolish.</b></font>

721
01:09:16,252 --> 01:09:18,286
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Where are you going?</b></font>

722
01:09:24,427 --> 01:09:26,928
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I saw pity in
your eyes for rhesus.</b></font>

723
01:09:27,096 --> 01:09:28,630
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Why?</b></font>

724
01:09:28,964 --> 01:09:30,198
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Look at me.</b></font>

725
01:09:30,200 --> 01:09:32,901
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Cotys is responsible
for this war, isn't he?</b></font>

726
01:09:36,105 --> 01:09:40,508
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You lie very well. Clearly,
your father's daughter.</b></font>

727
01:09:40,510 --> 01:09:44,879
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I didn't do it for my father.
I did it for my son.</b></font>

728
01:09:44,881 --> 01:09:49,551
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>If I disobeyed cotys or resisted
in any way, arius would be executed.</b></font>

729
01:09:49,553 --> 01:09:54,055
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I did what any mother would.
I protected my child.</b></font>

730
01:09:54,790 --> 01:09:56,958
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My husband was king.</b></font>

731
01:09:56,960 --> 01:10:00,028
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And cotys poisoned him
to take his place.</b></font>

732
01:10:00,030 --> 01:10:02,897
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Rhesus fought back.
Civil war broke out.</b></font>

733
01:10:02,899 --> 01:10:06,234
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Arius is the legitimate king.</b></font>

734
01:10:07,903 --> 01:10:09,437
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My father is old.</b></font>

735
01:10:09,439 --> 01:10:13,174
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He will not live forever,
and once he is gone,</b></font>

736
01:10:13,176 --> 01:10:16,744
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>my son will be a good king.</b></font>

737
01:10:17,112 --> 01:10:19,681
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And he will heal this land.</b></font>

738
01:10:19,683 --> 01:10:21,316
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>That's a dream.</b></font>

739
01:10:22,585 --> 01:10:23,751
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And you can help.</b></font>

740
01:10:23,753 --> 01:10:27,322
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Please, when you leave thrace,
take arius with you.</b></font>

741
01:10:27,324 --> 01:10:29,524
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Please keep him safe.</b></font>

742
01:10:30,059 --> 01:10:32,060
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Find another savior.</b></font>

743
01:10:32,161 --> 01:10:33,661
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules?</b></font>

744
01:10:35,464 --> 01:10:37,799
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The king
commands your presence.</b></font>

745
01:10:43,005 --> 01:10:44,572
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My lady.</b></font>

746
01:10:54,984 --> 01:10:57,385
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Ah, champion of thrace!</b></font>

747
01:10:57,387 --> 01:11:00,154
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Something tells me
we're not gonna get paid.</b></font>

748
01:11:00,256 --> 01:11:03,925
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- You could be right.
- Oh, shit.</b></font>

749
01:11:05,995 --> 01:11:09,264
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You wanted conquerors,
not heroes.</b></font>

750
01:11:09,266 --> 01:11:11,399
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You betrayed me, cotys.</b></font>

751
01:11:11,401 --> 01:11:13,268
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Betrayed?</b></font>

752
01:11:13,270 --> 01:11:17,438
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>A mercenary who has long since
sold his conscience for gold</b></font>

753
01:11:17,440 --> 01:11:20,642
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>can hardly presume to
judge his employers.</b></font>

754
01:11:20,644 --> 01:11:23,244
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Let's not
quibble about details.</b></font>

755
01:11:26,782 --> 01:11:31,753
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We all know your legend,
Hercules. But here is mine.</b></font>

756
01:11:31,755 --> 01:11:34,322
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>When I was a general
in the army of thrace,</b></font>

757
01:11:34,324 --> 01:11:37,425
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I had dreams of
ruling this kingdom.</b></font>

758
01:11:37,427 --> 01:11:40,795
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But thanks to you,
my dreams have grown.</b></font>

759
01:11:40,797 --> 01:11:43,431
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I now crave an empire.</b></font>

760
01:11:43,433 --> 01:11:48,736
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My thousands will train more
thousands, and they even more.</b></font>

761
01:11:48,738 --> 01:11:50,872
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The lessons of
Hercules will spread.</b></font>

762
01:11:50,874 --> 01:11:53,574
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What you began here
can never be stopped.</b></font>

763
01:11:53,576 --> 01:11:58,579
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And if you fear
what such an army may do,</b></font>

764
01:11:59,448 --> 01:12:01,182
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>then lead it.</b></font>

765
01:12:04,520 --> 01:12:08,356
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You want me to serve you?</b></font>

766
01:12:08,757 --> 01:12:11,893
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Spare me the moral outrage.</b></font>

767
01:12:12,294 --> 01:12:13,928
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Child killer.</b></font>

768
01:12:16,032 --> 01:12:19,867
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Getting us all killed,
bad idea.</b></font>

769
01:12:22,971 --> 01:12:27,275
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well,
I must take this as a "no."</b></font>

770
01:12:27,976 --> 01:12:29,610
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>In that case,</b></font>

771
01:12:30,379 --> 01:12:33,648
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>your services are
no longer required.</b></font>

772
01:12:36,952 --> 01:12:40,688
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You will be paid in full.
Bring them the gold.</b></font>

773
01:13:20,929 --> 01:13:26,100
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>If we hurry, we can be spending
our fortunes in Macedonia.</b></font>

774
01:13:29,238 --> 01:13:30,872
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Take mine, too.</b></font>

775
01:13:33,308 --> 01:13:36,144
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What do you think
you're doing? Let's go.</b></font>

776
01:13:36,146 --> 01:13:38,346
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>There will be no more
innocent blood on my hands.</b></font>

777
01:13:38,348 --> 01:13:41,816
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I can't leave
without setting this right.</b></font>

778
01:13:43,051 --> 01:13:43,751
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Oh, I see.</b></font>

779
01:13:43,753 --> 01:13:48,089
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And who's gonna be paying us
for this suicidal endeavor?</b></font>

780
01:13:48,091 --> 01:13:49,023
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Thrace needs our help.</b></font>

781
01:13:49,025 --> 01:13:51,726
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>To hell with thrace.
We have gold.</b></font>

782
01:13:52,361 --> 01:13:53,060
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You remember the black sea.</b></font>

783
01:13:53,062 --> 01:13:57,999
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>That beach you spoke of is
within reach. Leave now, be free.</b></font>

784
01:14:00,035 --> 01:14:02,403
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I would never be free.</b></font>

785
01:14:04,807 --> 01:14:07,475
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>In this fight, you're alone.</b></font>

786
01:14:09,611 --> 01:14:11,212
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Never saw that one coming.</b></font>

787
01:14:11,214 --> 01:14:13,915
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- How can you just walk away?
- You can't just leave.</b></font>

788
01:14:13,917 --> 01:14:15,550
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Why not?
- It's all right.</b></font>

789
01:14:15,552 --> 01:14:19,654
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You've sacrificed your lives for
me. Now you can finally be free.</b></font>

790
01:14:19,656 --> 01:14:22,690
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Whatever debt you feel
you owe me is paid.</b></font>

791
01:14:22,858 --> 01:14:24,425
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Debt?</b></font>

792
01:14:24,760 --> 01:14:28,696
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You think we follow you
because we owe you?</b></font>

793
01:14:29,331 --> 01:14:31,165
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Look around, Hercules.</b></font>

794
01:14:31,733 --> 01:14:33,634
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We're family.</b></font>

795
01:14:33,636 --> 01:14:36,070
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>All we have is each other.</b></font>

796
01:14:36,072 --> 01:14:40,975
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We will fight for you. And if
it's our time, we will die for you.</b></font>

797
01:14:40,977 --> 01:14:43,344
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Because you would die for us.</b></font>

798
01:14:45,280 --> 01:14:48,216
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Take that, too.
I have no need of it.</b></font>

799
01:14:48,817 --> 01:14:49,951
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>This is madness.</b></font>

800
01:14:49,953 --> 01:14:51,052
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You want madness?</b></font>

801
01:14:51,054 --> 01:14:55,323
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Tonight, a spear of flame
will Pierce my heart.</b></font>

802
01:14:55,924 --> 01:15:00,061
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Is that not the most insane
death you've ever heard of?</b></font>

803
01:15:10,038 --> 01:15:13,341
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Crazy. The lot of you.</b></font>

804
01:15:13,343 --> 01:15:15,042
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Autolycus.</b></font>

805
01:15:15,044 --> 01:15:18,679
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Iolaus. Go with autolycus.</b></font>

806
01:15:19,214 --> 01:15:20,615
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I think I'll stay.</b></font>

807
01:15:20,617 --> 01:15:20,915
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Nephew.</b></font>

808
01:15:20,917 --> 01:15:26,787
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Uncle, all I've ever done is tell stories
of great deeds performed by others.</b></font>

809
01:15:27,289 --> 01:15:32,293
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>It's time I stopped telling their
stories. Started living my own.</b></font>

810
01:15:32,295 --> 01:15:37,064
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well, you may have all completely
lost your minds, but not me.</b></font>

811
01:15:38,333 --> 01:15:39,901
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Not me.</b></font>

812
01:15:42,938 --> 01:15:44,305
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Autolycus?</b></font>

813
01:15:47,376 --> 01:15:49,911
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Live like a king, my friend.</b></font>

814
01:15:59,421 --> 01:16:01,222
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What about cotys?</b></font>

815
01:16:03,725 --> 01:16:06,060
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>He paid us to save thrace.</b></font>

816
01:16:06,062 --> 01:16:07,895
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Let's not disappoint him.</b></font>

817
01:16:36,658 --> 01:16:39,026
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Sitacles: Lay down your arms.</b></font>

818
01:16:40,562 --> 01:16:42,496
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Lay down your arms!</b></font>

819
01:16:42,664 --> 01:16:46,133
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Or your nephew dies first.</b></font>

820
01:17:01,350 --> 01:17:05,553
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I invite you to join me.
You refuse.</b></font>

821
01:17:05,555 --> 01:17:08,522
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I order you to leave.
You return.</b></font>

822
01:17:08,524 --> 01:17:11,959
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Get
your hands off me.</b></font>

823
01:17:13,195 --> 01:17:16,063
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I overheard her
conspiring with Hercules.</b></font>

824
01:17:16,065 --> 01:17:20,334
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>They were planning to remove the
young prince from your protection.</b></font>

825
01:17:25,340 --> 01:17:27,041
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No.</b></font>

826
01:17:27,209 --> 01:17:29,910
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Let go of him!
Don't touch him!</b></font>

827
01:17:33,415 --> 01:17:35,316
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Arius! No!</b></font>

828
01:17:39,055 --> 01:17:41,022
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No! You're hurting him! No!</b></font>

829
01:17:41,024 --> 01:17:43,624
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules, no!
Help me! Stop!</b></font>

830
01:17:43,626 --> 01:17:46,761
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Help! No!
- Ergenia: Arius. No.</b></font>

831
01:17:46,763 --> 01:17:49,063
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Arius! No!</b></font>

832
01:18:35,610 --> 01:18:38,646
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Magnificent, aren't they?</b></font>

833
01:18:39,014 --> 01:18:43,851
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>An extraordinary species.
Incredibly loyal.</b></font>

834
01:18:44,086 --> 01:18:46,554
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>As long as they're fed.</b></font>

835
01:18:46,556 --> 01:18:49,390
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Remember them?
- Eurystheus.</b></font>

836
01:18:50,625 --> 01:18:52,927
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>They remember you.</b></font>

837
01:18:53,028 --> 01:18:56,030
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Confused, Hercules?</b></font>

838
01:18:56,032 --> 01:19:01,802
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Kingdoms are won with armies,
but empires are made by alliances.</b></font>

839
01:19:01,804 --> 01:19:07,808
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>King eurystheus and I
will now rule all of Greece.</b></font>

840
01:19:13,682 --> 01:19:17,718
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Cerberus only
exists in my mind.</b></font>

841
01:19:18,587 --> 01:19:21,322
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Speak a little louder,
Hercules.</b></font>

842
01:19:22,190 --> 01:19:24,825
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I didn't quite catch that.</b></font>

843
01:19:26,628 --> 01:19:28,329
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The wolves.</b></font>

844
01:19:30,665 --> 01:19:32,900
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>They were there that night.</b></font>

845
01:19:33,235 --> 01:19:35,202
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>The wolves were there.</i></b></font>

846
01:19:35,204 --> 01:19:37,304
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>You drugged me.</i></b></font>

847
01:19:52,621 --> 01:19:56,657
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>The wolves were there the
night my family was murdered.</i></b></font>

848
01:19:59,594 --> 01:20:03,164
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My men told me
how your children screamed</b></font>

849
01:20:03,665 --> 01:20:06,901
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>as my wolves
gnawed on their bones.</b></font>

850
01:20:08,171 --> 01:20:12,339
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>As their fangs
despoiled your daughter's</b></font>

851
01:20:12,808 --> 01:20:14,241
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>pure flesh.</b></font>

852
01:20:14,409 --> 01:20:18,445
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>When the people called out
your name louder than mine,</b></font>

853
01:20:18,447 --> 01:20:21,782
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>you see,
when they saw you as a God,</b></font>

854
01:20:21,784 --> 01:20:24,518
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>how long before
they saw you as their king?</b></font>

855
01:20:24,520 --> 01:20:25,452
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I wanted nothing!</b></font>

856
01:20:25,454 --> 01:20:29,023
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Precisely! Your sin, Hercules,
was that you had no ambition!</b></font>

857
01:20:29,025 --> 01:20:32,159
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I can deal with an ambitious
man! He can be bought!</b></font>

858
01:20:32,161 --> 01:20:35,830
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But a man who wants nothing
has no price!</b></font>

859
01:20:36,998 --> 01:20:40,634
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Killing you would have
turned Athens against me.</b></font>

860
01:20:40,969 --> 01:20:42,803
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I had to ruin your name.</b></font>

861
01:20:46,741 --> 01:20:48,309
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My wife!</b></font>

862
01:20:49,277 --> 01:20:50,010
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My children!</b></font>

863
01:20:50,012 --> 01:20:53,047
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well, you have our permission
to join them in death.</b></font>

864
01:20:53,049 --> 01:20:58,419
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>All of you! Starting with
my faithless daughter!</b></font>

865
01:20:58,653 --> 01:21:01,155
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No! Get off me!</b></font>

866
01:21:01,423 --> 01:21:03,891
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No! No! No!</b></font>

867
01:21:03,893 --> 01:21:06,360
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Unhand me! No!</b></font>

868
01:21:06,362 --> 01:21:07,862
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>She's your own
flesh and blood!</b></font>

869
01:21:07,864 --> 01:21:10,164
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I will raise arius to be
my worthy successor!</b></font>

870
01:21:10,166 --> 01:21:15,369
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You stay away from my boy!
You monster, you bastard!</b></font>

871
01:21:15,371 --> 01:21:18,772
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- You are a monster! You are a monster!
- No!</b></font>

872
01:21:18,774 --> 01:21:21,575
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You are not a man!</b></font>

873
01:21:21,577 --> 01:21:23,377
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're a demon!</b></font>

874
01:21:23,379 --> 01:21:25,379
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Who are you?</b></font>

875
01:21:25,680 --> 01:21:26,814
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Are you a murderer?</b></font>

876
01:21:26,816 --> 01:21:29,016
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Damn you! I curse you!</b></font>

877
01:21:29,018 --> 01:21:32,152
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Are you a mercenary who turns
his back on the innocent?</b></font>

878
01:21:32,154 --> 01:21:33,587
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Stay away from my son!</b></font>

879
01:21:33,589 --> 01:21:35,222
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Are you only the legend?</b></font>

880
01:21:35,224 --> 01:21:38,726
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Or are you
the truth behind the legend?</b></font>

881
01:21:38,728 --> 01:21:40,694
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No! Father,
please, please, please.</b></font>

882
01:21:40,696 --> 01:21:42,663
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We believe in you.</b></font>

883
01:21:43,231 --> 01:21:45,199
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>We have faith in you.</b></font>

884
01:21:45,201 --> 01:21:46,967
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Have faith in yourself.</b></font>

885
01:21:46,969 --> 01:21:48,035
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Save me!</b></font>

886
01:21:48,037 --> 01:21:49,470
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Amphiaraus: Remember the man
that you are.</b></font>

887
01:21:49,472 --> 01:21:53,474
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Father, the gods will punish
you! You cannot escape this time!</b></font>

888
01:21:53,476 --> 01:21:55,943
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Remember the deeds
you have performed,</b></font>

889
01:21:55,945 --> 01:21:57,978
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>the labors you
have accomplished!</b></font>

890
01:21:58,747 --> 01:22:00,314
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No! No!</b></font>

891
01:22:00,316 --> 01:22:02,082
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Stop it!
- Leave her alone!</b></font>

892
01:22:02,084 --> 01:22:04,551
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Now, tell me!</b></font>

893
01:22:04,553 --> 01:22:05,552
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Please!</b></font>

894
01:22:05,554 --> 01:22:08,255
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Who are you?</b></font>

895
01:22:08,257 --> 01:22:12,660
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I am Hercules!</b></font>

896
01:22:22,370 --> 01:22:25,339
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Unleash the wolves!</b></font>

897
01:22:29,378 --> 01:22:30,711
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Get away!</b></font>

898
01:22:30,713 --> 01:22:32,379
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Ahh!</b></font>

899
01:22:38,687 --> 01:22:42,656
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Three wolves should be
more than enough for one lion.</b></font>

900
01:22:44,025 --> 01:22:45,826
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Ahh!</b></font>

901
01:22:45,828 --> 01:22:47,394
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hurry!</b></font>

902
01:22:53,368 --> 01:22:54,902
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Hurry!
- Hurry!</b></font>

903
01:22:57,339 --> 01:22:58,572
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No!</b></font>

904
01:23:10,085 --> 01:23:11,685
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Ahh!</b></font>

905
01:23:25,200 --> 01:23:27,668
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The gods have
revealed your innocence.</b></font>

906
01:23:27,670 --> 01:23:30,637
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>The final labor is complete.</b></font>

907
01:23:30,639 --> 01:23:33,007
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But I'm just getting started.</b></font>

908
01:23:39,547 --> 01:23:43,283
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Doesn't take a vision to know
what's waiting for us up there.</b></font>

909
01:24:12,580 --> 01:24:14,148
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>My time.</b></font>

910
01:24:24,526 --> 01:24:27,761
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Excuse me.
That was my moment, my fate.</b></font>

911
01:24:27,829 --> 01:24:29,630
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're welcome.</b></font>

912
01:24:41,576 --> 01:24:44,545
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I'm going after eurystheus!</b></font>

913
01:25:05,066 --> 01:25:08,368
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules, listen to me.
None of this is my fault.</b></font>

914
01:25:08,370 --> 01:25:10,604
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You see,
cotys poisoned my mind.</b></font>

915
01:25:10,606 --> 01:25:13,507
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Turned me against you.</b></font>

916
01:25:13,509 --> 01:25:14,908
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I like you.</b></font>

917
01:25:14,910 --> 01:25:15,509
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No, stop.</b></font>

918
01:25:15,511 --> 01:25:19,646
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I command you to stop! I'm your
king! You took an oath to obey me!</b></font>

919
01:25:19,648 --> 01:25:21,982
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You swore to Zeus!</b></font>

920
01:25:21,984 --> 01:25:23,517
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Wait, wait, wait.</b></font>

921
01:25:23,618 --> 01:25:27,921
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You fight for gold. I have
plenty of gold. Name your price.</b></font>

922
01:25:27,923 --> 01:25:31,058
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Find it in your
heart to forgive.</b></font>

923
01:25:35,997 --> 01:25:38,398
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You want forgiveness?</b></font>

924
01:25:53,982 --> 01:25:56,850
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Ask my family for forgiveness.</b></font>

925
01:26:14,736 --> 01:26:17,604
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I've never
killed a God before.</b></font>

926
01:26:26,714 --> 01:26:29,716
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>I really think I'm
ready to fight now.</b></font>

927
01:26:33,488 --> 01:26:35,389
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Well done, warrior.</b></font>

928
01:26:47,168 --> 01:26:48,569
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Eurystheus?
- Dead.</b></font>

929
01:26:48,571 --> 01:26:51,605
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- We need to find arius.
- Hercules: Follow me.</b></font>

930
01:27:05,920 --> 01:27:07,387
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Soldiers of thrace!</b></font>

931
01:27:07,389 --> 01:27:11,892
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You followed me in battle.
Follow me now.</b></font>

932
01:27:11,960 --> 01:27:13,427
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Don't be fools!</b></font>

933
01:27:13,429 --> 01:27:17,097
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules is mortal! Not a God!</b></font>

934
01:27:17,232 --> 01:27:21,735
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Anyone who sides
with him will die!</b></font>

935
01:27:22,570 --> 01:27:24,905
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>And I will show you.</b></font>

936
01:27:25,006 --> 01:27:26,640
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Bring him.</b></font>

937
01:27:30,545 --> 01:27:32,045
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>- Arius!
- Mama!</b></font>

938
01:27:32,047 --> 01:27:34,648
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>No! He's your grandson!</b></font>

939
01:27:34,650 --> 01:27:37,484
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You failed to save
your children, Hercules.</b></font>

940
01:27:37,486 --> 01:27:39,953
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>But you may yet save him.</b></font>

941
01:27:39,955 --> 01:27:41,555
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Please, father! No!</b></font>

942
01:27:41,723 --> 01:27:43,657
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Admit defeat!</b></font>

943
01:27:43,891 --> 01:27:45,659
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Bow to me!</b></font>

944
01:27:45,994 --> 01:27:49,796
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You have until
the count of three!</b></font>

945
01:27:52,066 --> 01:27:54,001
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>One!</b></font>

946
01:27:54,836 --> 01:27:55,469
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Two!</b></font>

947
01:27:58,306 --> 01:28:00,874
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Don't just stand there!
Kill someone!</b></font>

948
01:28:02,010 --> 01:28:03,944
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Protect lord cotys!</b></font>

949
01:28:06,948 --> 01:28:08,382
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Arius, run!</b></font>

950
01:28:08,384 --> 01:28:09,683
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Mother!</b></font>

951
01:28:10,652 --> 01:28:12,019
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Get the boy!</b></font>

952
01:28:52,860 --> 01:28:54,828
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Ahh!</b></font>

953
01:29:05,506 --> 01:29:07,207
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Tydeus!</b></font>

954
01:29:09,644 --> 01:29:12,346
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Attack!</b></font>

955
01:29:12,348 --> 01:29:14,247
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hold them back!</b></font>

956
01:29:29,831 --> 01:29:31,631
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Spears!</b></font>

957
01:29:36,638 --> 01:29:38,472
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Go through the fire!</b></font>

958
01:29:43,711 --> 01:29:47,180
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Here! Here! Help! Come on!</b></font>

959
01:29:50,952 --> 01:29:52,619
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Easy, tydeus.</b></font>

960
01:30:22,984 --> 01:30:24,384
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules.</b></font>

961
01:30:45,039 --> 01:30:46,740
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Lock shields!</b></font>

962
01:30:47,809 --> 01:30:49,576
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>March!</b></font>

963
01:30:51,579 --> 01:30:53,613
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Find peace, my brother.</b></font>

964
01:31:08,429 --> 01:31:14,601
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>As you said, Hercules, there is
no way to defeat a shield wall!</b></font>

965
01:31:14,836 --> 01:31:17,404
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>There is no way out!</b></font>

966
01:31:18,172 --> 01:31:20,540
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Come out and face me!</b></font>

967
01:31:27,281 --> 01:31:30,951
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're no hero! You're no God!</b></font>

968
01:31:30,953 --> 01:31:33,386
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>You're nothing
but a mercenary!</b></font>

969
01:31:33,388 --> 01:31:37,257
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Your wife and
children deserved to die!</b></font>

970
01:31:59,180 --> 01:32:00,447
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>What're you doing?</b></font>

971
01:32:00,449 --> 01:32:02,449
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Get back up there!</b></font>

972
01:32:02,451 --> 01:32:05,552
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules must die!</b></font>

973
01:32:08,122 --> 01:32:09,823
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Come on!</b></font>

974
01:32:11,459 --> 01:32:15,295
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Kill that filthy bastard!</b></font>

975
01:33:14,322 --> 01:33:17,891
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules! Hercules!</b></font>

976
01:33:18,025 --> 01:33:21,528
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules! Hercules!</b></font>

977
01:33:21,530 --> 01:33:27,033
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules! Hercules! Hercules!</b></font>

978
01:33:27,035 --> 01:33:30,637
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules! Hercules!</b></font>

979
01:33:30,639 --> 01:33:40,213
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b>Hercules! Hercules! Hercules!</b></font>

980
01:33:40,215 --> 01:33:44,250
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>You want to know
the truth about Hercules?</i></b></font>

981
01:33:44,252 --> 01:33:46,086
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>There it is.</i></b></font>

982
01:33:46,088 --> 01:33:50,357
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>To be honest,
I prefer it to the legend.</i></b></font>

983
01:33:50,359 --> 01:33:54,561
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>The world needs a hero
they can believe in.</i></b></font>

984
01:33:54,629 --> 01:33:58,331
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>Is he actually
the son of Zeus?</i></b></font>

985
01:33:58,333 --> 01:34:01,134
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>I don't think it
really matters.</i></b></font>

986
01:34:01,136 --> 01:34:04,838
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>You don't need to be
a demigod to be a hero.</i></b></font>

987
01:34:04,840 --> 01:34:08,408
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>You just need to
believe you're a hero.</i></b></font>

988
01:34:08,410 --> 01:34:11,578
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>It's what worked for him.</i></b></font>

989
01:34:12,313 --> 01:34:17,350
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>But then again,
what the hell do I know?</i></b></font>

990
01:34:17,518 --> 01:34:20,754
<font face="Comic Sans MS" color="#ffff80"><b><i>I'm supposed to
be dead by now.</i></b></font>

